data.description: Do not let the pictures of this truly AMAZING property fool you!!! They are great pics, but it extremely needs to be seen in person to appreciate!  When you drive up to the solar gated fenced front entrance is where the experience of being impressed starts!  The front yard is completely and tastefully fenced with drive thru and walk thru entrances and sprinklers for the lawn area.   After entering the gates straight ahead is a work shop/garage that is set with electrical and complete drive thru abilities to the back yard and out of the property.  The home has a new HVAC unit that was installed 2 years ago, new flooring, new paint, new hot water heater, and much more!  What makes this property so desirable is the fact that you can access the drive thru fences from either Hwy 41, Granite Dell, or from the front.  There is also another dog run set up inside of the fenced back yard. The front and back yard are completely fenced so it makes it perfect for the kids and fur babies.  The garage was converted by a licensed contractor into another larger bedroom and closet.  Do not forget that the property is surrounded by other gorgeous homes making this a perfect place to call home!!!!!
